The Building

Introducing 12 Newcastle St,  a prominent and modern 4 Level, office building in the rapidly evolving northern fringe of the Perth CBD. 

12 Newcastle is owned and managed by Dorado Property who have built a reputation for being relationship focussed and committed to offering a professional and proactive experience for tenants.

Capital Works Program

Dorado is completing an extensive refurbishment program at the building. 
•	Lobby - COMPLETED
•	Market Leading Fitouts - COMPLETED
•	New Exterior Facade - WORKS COMMENCING JUNE 2021 

The new fitouts feature architecturally designed space with reception areas, meeting rooms, kitchen, workstations, breakout areas and furniture. Currently available space includes;

Level 2 - 627sqm

Other Key benefits offered by 12 Newcastle St are:

•	5 Star NABERS rating
•	High parking ratio and surrounding carpark availability
•	Floor to Ceiling Windows with views out to Perth Hills
•	Close proximity to all public transport connections
•	Walking distance to Northbridge Food and entertainment
•	High profile signage available
•	Hands-on and customer focused owner/ manager

Secure car parking bays are available at $300 per bay per month plus DOT Levy and GST.

Outgoings are estimated at a $150.00/sqm for FY22

Please contact the leasing agents to arrange an inspection
